            <p class="text-indigo-100 text-lg italic">Analytický nástroj pro interpretaci kognitivního zkreslení a strachu z chyby</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-4">
                
                <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-200 shadow-sm">
                    <h2 class="text-sm font-bold text-indigo-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Příprava měření</h2>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                        Nejprve si stáhněte šablonu dotazníku. Po vyplnění žáky získáte průměrné hodnoty v propojené tabulce (v listu „PRO UČITELE“).
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1RyEEQxY7NjpeyIjpYVqA6xJImYE_QCTxJFSeLPlbAYU/copy" target="_blank" 
                       class="block text-center bg-indigo-600 text-white hover:bg-indigo-700 font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md active:scale-95 text-sm">
                        Stáhnout šablonu dotazníku
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-slate-200 h-fit">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center text-indigo-900">
                        <span class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 w-8 h-8 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2 text-sm">2</span>
                        Vyhodnocení
                    </h2>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-5">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1 leading-tight">Průměr TEORIE<br><span class="text-[10px] font-normal text-slate-500">(Otázka 1: Chyba je špatná)</span></label>
                            <input type="number" id="teorie" step="0.1" min="1" max="5" placeholder="Např. 2.1"
                                class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none transition bg-white text-slate-900">
                        </div>
                        
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1 leading-tight">Průměr PRAXE<br><span class="text-[10px] font-normal text-slate-500">(Otázky 2+3: Emoce a strach)</span></label>
                            <input type="number" id="praxe" step="0.1" min="1" max="5" placeholder="Např. 3.8"
                                class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none transition bg-white text-slate-900">
                        </div>

                        <button onclick="vypocitej()" 
                            class="w-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-all active:scale-95 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">
                            Zobrazit výsledky
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
                
                <div id="vysledek-placeholder" class="bg-white border-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-16 text-center text-slate-400">
                    <svg class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
                    Zadejte průměrné hodnoty pro zobrazení diagnózy.
                </div>

                <div id="vysledek-box" class="hidden bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-l-8 transition-all transform duration-500">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                        <h2 id="diagnoza-title" class="text-2xl font-bold"></h2>
                        <span id="badge-rozkol" class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase"></span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p id="rozkol-info" class="text-slate-600 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed"></p>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 border-b pb-2 text-indigo-900">Navržené intervence</h3>
                    <div id="metody-container" class="space-y-4 text-slate-900"></div>
                </div>

            </div>
